Package: taxreturn
Title: An R package for retrieving and curating public DNA barcode reference data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Alexander",
           family = "Piper",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "alexander.piper@agriculture.vic.gov.au",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0664-7564"))
Description: taxreturn is an R package for fetching DNA barcode sequences and associated taxonomic annotations from public databases such as the Barcode of Life Database (BOLD) and NCBI GenBank, curating these sequences and formatting them into training sets compatible with popular taxonomic classifiers used for metabarcoding and marker gene analysis.
